Name: Scullin
Description: The Division of Scullin consists of part of the Whittlesea City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Manufacturing, light industrial, food processing, packaging and distribution, health and education.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of the Rt Hon. James Henry Scullin, 1876-1953. Scullin was Prime Minister of Australia (1929-32) and a Member of the House of Representatives (1910-13 and 1922-49).
